name: [GRB]-#2022
description:
awe-inspiring Cosmic graphics in Sci-fi dreams.
Digitally to create a psychedelic synthesizer symphony of modern Technicolor. 

The girl subjects reflect on how small we truly are in this vast universe. 
In every corner of the globe, following you, watching, waiting.
Reminding us of what we need to remember. Of what we can, and should be.
Reminds us of those more charming futures–of those hopeful expectations we’d forgotten–in the quaint imaginations of yesterday. "The Sci-Fi Future has not yet arrived". So enjoy the expanse, feeling joy, tranquility, freedom, and power. As a result, we feel the same.
